This chart has been prepared from the contents of Dr Grey Wolf's head, in the style of an RYA Training
Chart, oh, and just for fun, includes a loose adaptation of the OS Map of Brownsea Island for the training
and entertainment of SeaScouts. It is almost entierly ficticious and therefore cannot be used for navigation.
NOT TO BE USED FOR NAVIGATON
NOT TO BE USED FOR NAVIGATON
Created by Grey Wolf AKA Mike Jones primarily for the education and entertainment of Scouts and leaders associated with Sea Scouting.
This map is largely fictional. It was created based on the RYA3 and Admiralty training map with symbols to resemble IALA buoyage and
landmarks on charts generally available on the market. The map provides oportunity to use simple navigational concepts as part of an
escape room activity. If you have enjoyed this you might like to buymeacoffee.com/emceearsey . CC BY-NC-SA
